								<wikidot:authorUserId>6315381</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I quite like this SCP. It is a fun concept, but i would’ve liked to see a bit more of an explanation as to how the entity's anomalous properties worked. That being Said when i read it i liked it, but it could definitely be improved upon. as with all works of fiction. Abstain for now.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
