					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I dig this entry! I'm a fan of anything that screws with the &quot;entity tries to escape, Foundation keeps it in&quot; standard, but something about this particular set-up achieves a certain delightful absurdism when it comes to the disconnect between the Foundation and the Man in Khakis. +1 from me!</p> 
				 	]]>
